{
  "stem": "18470.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I did manage to publish two or three articles a year, mostly written in Israel, and a book or two.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I want to do some more serious work in the areas I have begun, namely the-- the origins development of Zionism and its-- and its changing modalities and meaning for our world today.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- in 1979, President Carter, at the instigation of Elie Wiesel, appointed a presidential commission on the Holocaust, a committee really, for the purposes of developing a memorial in the United States for the victims of the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And part of the mandate was to travel through Eastern Europe to see memorials, to note what had been done, and then come back with a recommendation to the president.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to Poland, started out with going to Warsaw and Treblinka, Auschwitz, then to Babi Yar, Kiev, Moscow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we came back via Amsterdam and then Israel, Yad Vashem.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we came back with a recommendation that no monument be erected.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the president had in mind a monument,",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--statuary, you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that, in place of a monument, important as such, a memorial would be there be a living memorial in the form of either an archive library and museum complex or one of the above mentioned.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came back with that as our recommendation, presented it to President Carter at the White House.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I have a photograph of that presentation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the Carter administration said, thank you very much, but we have no place in Washington that we can offer you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There is some land out in Virginia somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we said, give us a chance to look.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the committee delegated the responsibility to three knowledgeable people, and they found some ramshackle old buildings near the Treasury.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
